### Create Event

POST http://localhost:5500/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "React Workshop",
    "description": "A hands-on workshop to learn the basics of React.js and build your first web app.",
    "date": "2026-04-10T10:00:00.000Z",
    "location": "Tech Hub, San Francisco, CA"
  }

### Get all events
GET http://localhost:5500/api/events


